Nina Vale https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Nina_Vale 0 Nina Vale was an American actress and dancer, who had three leading roles in films of the 1940s, but stopped acting for unknown reasons. Vale only acted in three movies. It is not known why she didn't appear in any others.
